== Amashuri yize. ==
Mu 1995-2000, Rwakazina Marie Chantal yabonye impanya bushobozi yikiciro cya mbere cya kaminuza ibutare mubijyanye  nubukungu (bachelor's degree in economics)(2001-2003)yabonye Kandi impanya bushobozi yikiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza yakuye muri kaminuza ya fondation Universtaire Luxembourgeoise,arlon Belgium.

== Urugendo mu miyoborere. ==
